def tags_f(args: argparse.Namespace) -> None:

    from .tags import tags



    names = (

        tags(

            wheel,

            args.python_tag,

            args.abi_tag,

            args.platform_tag,

            args.build,

            args.remove,

        )

        for wheel in args.wheel

    )



    for name in names:

        print(name)
